headline: Simon® Acquires Phillips Place in Charlotte
summary: Simon®, a real estate investment trust engaged in the ownership of premier shopping, dining, entertainment and mixed-use destinations, today announced that it has acquired Phillips Place™ in the heart of the SouthPark neighborhood of Charlotte, North Carolina.
